"Python programs. Check out `Django Packages <https://djangopackages.org>`_ "
"for existing reusable apps you could incorporate in your project. Django "
"itself is also just a Python package. This means that you can take existing "
"Python packages or Django apps and compose them into your own web project. "
"You only need to write the parts that make your project unique."
msgstr ""

